      <p class="entitled">entitled</p>
      <longTitle>
        <p>An Act to end religious discrimination in admission to primary and post-primary <eol/>educational establishments and to provide for full participation of pupils of all faiths and <eol/>none in primary and post-primary educational establishments.</p>
      </longTitle>
    </preface>
